== GNOME to Trusty (in launchpad) ==

This is a list mapping gnome modules from the damned lies website to the locations that they can be translated for trusty in launchpad. This way teams can keep those translations in sync.

=== GNOME 3.10 ===

Those are the GNOME modules, ordered as they appear in the <nowiki>[[http://l10n.gnome.org/releases/gnome-3-10/|GNOME 3.10 (UI) module set]]</nowiki> page.
